Payton Haas https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Payton_Haas 0 Payton Haas (born June 9, 1979) is an American actor who is most known for starring as Mike Blondel in the first season of Flipper, alongside Jessica Alba, Brian Wimmer, and Colleen Flynn. Haas is a 2004 graduate in Computer and Information Sciences from the University of Florida.
